{
  "_doc": "Soundness policy for the self-growing taxonomy (docs/anima-knowledge-graph.md §self-evolution). The KGE coherence gate proves a deduction RESOLVES, not that the premises are MEANINGFUL — so a noisy/vandalized Wikidata P279 edge could otherwise certify 'Einstein is a being/subject/proto-agent/robot'. This policy is an independent guard: at ingest we DROP edges that climb into abstract upper-ontology nodes (so 'person' is the meaningful ceiling) and break cycles/self-loops; at deduction time a generalization only COUNTS if its target is a certified type. Edit this, not the code.",
